'''Skraup合成'''（Skraup synthesis），又称'''Skraup反应'''，以捷克化学家 Zdenko Hans Skraup (1850－1910) 的名字命名。

[[苯胺|苯胺]]（或其他[[芳基|芳]][[胺|胺]]）与[[硫酸|硫酸]]、[[甘油|甘油]]和[[氧化剂|氧化剂]]如[[硝基苯|硝基苯]]（也是溶剂）共热时，得到[[喹啉|喹啉]]。<ref>{{cite journal en| author = Skraup, Z. H. | title = Eine Synthese des Chinolins | journal = [[Berichte|Berichte]] | year = 1880 | volume = 13 | pages = 2086}}</ref><ref> {{cite journal en| author = Manske, R. H. F. | journal = [[Chem._Rev.|Chem. Rev.]] | year = 1942 | volume = 30 | pages = 113 | doi = 10.1021/cr60095a006 | title = The Chemistry of Quinolines.}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en| author =  Manske, R. H. F.; Kulka, M. | journal = [[Org._React.|Org. React.]] | year = 1953 | volume = 7 | pages = 80–99}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal en| author = Wahren, M. | journal = [[Tetrahedron_(journal)|Tetrahedron]] | year = 1964 | volume = 20 | pages = 2773 | doi = 10.1016/S0040-4020(01)98495-9 | title = Stabilisotop markierte verbindungen—II , Untersuchung der skraupschen chinolin-synthese mit hilfe von 15N| url = https://archive.org/details/sim_tetrahedron_1964_20/page/2773 }}</ref>

